        <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-300 mb-8">About</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            George has over 10 years of experience leading customer relationships, strategic initiatives,
            and transformation programmes across fintech, Web3, and enterprise technology.
          </p>
          <p>
            Most recently, he led strategic partnerships and ecosystem growth at SideShift.ai. Prior to
            that, he served as Chief of Staff to programme leadership at Accenture on a major FTSE 100
            transformation programme for Kingfisher Group, acting as the bridge between executive
            stakeholders and delivery teams. His background combines customer success, partnerships,
            programme leadership, and enterprise consulting, with a strong track record of growing
            accounts, delivering complex initiatives, and building trusted stakeholder relationships.
          </p>
          <p>Based in Thailand, he is open to remote and hybrid opportunities.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

